{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"admin","authorName":"孙天骁","classify":"其他","content":"<p>hi！大家好！孙天骁的个人网站经过长时间的建设，已经形成了自己的特色。作为本网站的站长，我很欢迎大家来我的网站做客！</p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">网站特色展示</span></span></strong></p><hr /><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">1.首页动态展示</span></u></span></strong></p><p><a href=\"/Files/image/xc/1.png\"><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/1.png\" width=\"370\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" /></a></p><p>通过手机客户端，我经常发布动态，多数动态将实时展现在首页，供来访者更加深入了解我。</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2.首页图片展示</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/2.png\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>通过图片记录生活，随时更新，供来访者更加了解我身边的一切。</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">3.首页格言警示</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/3.png\" width=\"591\" height=\"165\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>每次光临，都会送你一条格言。愿你在阅读之中能有所收获。</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">4.强大的文章创作系统</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/4.png\" width=\"528\" height=\"217\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>每个人都能在网站上写文章，每个人都可以为网站贡献内容！</p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/11.png\" width=\"621\" height=\"383\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>文章页已支持评论！</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">5.精致的朋友介绍页面</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/5.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"416\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>每个朋友都配有介绍，通过随记来使你们更加了解我的朋友和我的关系！希望我的朋友也能与你成为朋友！</p><p>每个条目都有灰色的心<img src=\"/Files/image/xc/6.png\" width=\"90\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" />点击可以点亮红心！<img src=\"/Files/image/xc/7.png\" width=\"86\" height=\"70\" alt=\"\" /></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">6.精致的新版网站留言板</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/8.png\" width=\"676\" height=\"318\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>认证功能，把你百度的头像搬过来！楼中楼，让留言板变得更加生动！</p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/9.png\" width=\"698\" height=\"221\" alt=\"\" /></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">7.强大的网站管理后台</span></u></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/Files/image/xc/10.png\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>前台的强大，必然对应着后台的强大！你想成为本站管理员吗？</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 153);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 153, 102);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">牢记我们的网址：</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 153);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 153, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.ybusad.com\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">www.ybusad.com</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">！</span></strong></span></span></p>","createTime":"2013-07-19 20:25:47","customCoverKey":"","id":28,"isGood":false,"isTop":false,"publicState":0,"replyCount":0,"state":0,"tags":["作品展示"],"title":"《孙天骁的小站 宣传小册》","urlCode":"UT1SG5NCWO","viewCount":295,"viewGroup":-1,"authPassed":true},"author":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}}